---
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Oracle EPM Cloud Blog" description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<h1>About This Blog</h1>
	<p>
		Welcome to the Oracle EPM Cloud Blog. This site is dedicated to helping Oracle EPM Cloud
		professionals stay up to date with the latest product updates, tutorials, tips, and real-world
		use cases across EPM Cloud Updates, Narrative Reporting, and Planning Cloud.
	</p>
	<p>
		Whether you are just getting started or are a seasoned EPM administrator, you will find
		practical content to help you get the most out of Oracle's Enterprise Performance Management
		Cloud platform.
	</p>
</BaseLayout>
